/user/api/login/=== to get the access tokens and logging in
/user/api/register/ === sign up
/api/ === products listing
/api/<int:pk>/ === products details

/blog/api/ === blog post listing and creating post
/blog/api/create/ === creates a post
/blog/api/update/<int:id>/ to update a blog
/blog/api/<int:id/ === to see a blog details


